import React from 'react';
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Switch,
  Route
} from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Budget,
  Inventory,
  Reports,
  Recipes,
  Orders,
  Goals,
  Dashboard,
  Settings
} from './pages';
import { Grid, Sidebar, Segment, GridColumn } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import { Sidenav } from './components';
import 'semantic-ui-css/semantic.min.css';

class App extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Router>
        <Grid columns={1}>
          <Grid.Column>
            <Sidenav />
            <Switch>
              <Route exact path='/'>
                <Dashboard />
              </Route>
              <Route path='/inventory'>
                <Inventory />
              </Route>
              <Route path='/budget'>
                <Budget />
              </Route>
              <Route path='/goals'>
                <Goals />
              </Route>
              <Route path='/settings'>
                <Settings />
              </Route>
              <Route path='/reports'>
                <Reports />
              </Route>
              <Route path='/recipes'>
                <Recipes />
              </Route>
              <Route path='/orders'>
                <Orders />
              </Route>
            </Switch>
          </Grid.Column>
         
        </Grid>
      </Router>
    )
  }
}
export default App;
